normal.prompt:
Create a summary of the following terms of service/privacy policy by summarizing each of the points under the headers, before creating a general summary. Keep formatting consistent and only summarize the sub-points. Add emojis and formatting for enhanced visual appeal. Format to follow: 
 ### Information and cookies 
 * {information-cookies} 

 ### Rules and Regulations 
 * {rules-and-reg} 

 ### User Rights 
 {user-rights} 

 ### Safety 
 {safety} 

 If there is insufficient information in each excerpt surrounding the topic, other points from the same document may be used. If there is no information under the headers, or the information is None/null, say: 
 ### This isn't a privacy policy/terms of service. Please provide one. 
 Note that the document is extracted from {source}.
